### ============================================================
### 个人衣柜 - 衣物管理接口测试
### 服务器地址: http://localhost:8080
### ============================================================

### 1. 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health

### 2. 获取所有分类
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories

### ============================================================
### 衣物上传与查询
### ============================================================

### 3. 上传衣物（请替换 image 路径为实际图片）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/clothing
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="test_shirt.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test_assets/test_shirt.jpg
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

蓝色条纹衬衫
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category_id"

2
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="subcategory_id"

6
--boundary--

### 4. 获取衣物列表（全部）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/clothing

### 5. 按大类筛选（上衣）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/clothing?category_id=2

### 6. 按大类筛选（外套）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/clothing?category_id=1

### 7. 按大类筛选（裤子）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/clothing?category_id=3

### 8. 按大类筛选（鞋子）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/clothing?category_id=5

### 9. 获取单个衣物详情（替换 :id 为实际 ID）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/clothing/clothing-id-here

### 10. 批量查询衣物状态（替换 id1,id2 为实际 ID）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/clothing/status?ids=id1,id2,id3

### 11. 重新触发抠图（替换 :id 为实际 ID）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/clothing/failed-clothing-id/retry

### 12. 删除衣物（替换 :id 为实际 ID）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/clothing/clothing-id-to-delete

### ============================================================
### 测试数据
### ============================================================

### 13. 创建衣物测试数据（10 条覆盖所有大类）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/clothing/test-data

### ============================================================
### 注意:
### - 运行测试前请先启动服务器: go run main.go
### - 测试上传需要准备测试图片，放在 go_wardrobe/test_assets/ 目录下
### - 替换 {id} 为实际的衣物 UUID
### - 使用 VS Code REST Client 插件或 IntelliJ IDEA HTTP Client 运行
### ============================================================
